OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FWind easing
OL,6,Fa little this evening, but mostly dry
OL,7,Fwith sunny spells, although isolated
OL,8,Fshowers are possible in the north.
OL,9,FBreezy overnight, and dry with clear
OL,10,Fspells.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FDry with sunny spells at
OL,13,Ffirst, but becoming more cloudy and
OL,14,Fwindy in the north of the region
OL,15,Fduring the morning. Brighter in the
OL,16,Fsouth. Feeling cool in the wind.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
